332
00:23:29,066 --> 00:23:31,704
This bloody savagery is unbelievable!

333
00:23:31,729 --> 00:23:34,182
Oh, no! Tarakus!

334
00:23:34,207 --> 00:23:35,811
Pathetic waste of flesh!

335
00:23:35,836 --> 00:23:37,692
